text: Prakash Jaganath Fadte is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Goa Legislative Assembly from Maem in the 1999 Goa Legislative Assembly election as a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. He was Minister of Education, Science and Technology and Printing and Stationery in Francisco Sardinha cabinet from November 1999 to October 2000.My NetaGoa Govt reduced to minorityRealignment of forces likely in GoaFormer Goa MLAs announce formation of new political party ==References== Category:1954 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Members of the Goa Legislative Assembly Category:People from North Goa district Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians from Goa Category:United Goans Democratic Party politicians
